## Example Commands

### Basic Operations

```bash
# List resources
python .claude/skills/{{TOPIC}}-{skill}/scripts/list_{resource}.py

# Get a specific resource
python .claude/skills/{{TOPIC}}-{skill}/scripts/get_{resource}.py ID

# Create a resource
python .claude/skills/{{TOPIC}}-{skill}/scripts/create_{resource}.py \
  --name "Name" --description "Description"

# Update a resource
python .claude/skills/{{TOPIC}}-{skill}/scripts/update_{resource}.py ID \
  --name "New Name"

# Delete a resource
python .claude/skills/{{TOPIC}}-{skill}/scripts/delete_{resource}.py ID
```

### Search Operations

```bash
# Basic search
python .claude/skills/{{TOPIC}}-search/scripts/search.py "query"

# With filters
python .claude/skills/{{TOPIC}}-search/scripts/search.py "query" \
  --type resource --status active
```

## Configuration

### Multiple Profiles

```json
{
  "{{TOPIC}}": {
    "default_profile": "production",
    "profiles": {
      "production": {
        "url": "https://api.example.com",
        "default_project": "PROD"
      },
      "development": {
        "url": "https://api-dev.example.com",
        "default_project": "DEV"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Use profiles:

```bash
python script.py --profile development
```

